T02TD2124E:170b-1: shr'i bha ga w'an ae ka dz'a ti s'a dha nam /
T02TD2124E:170b-3: dpal bcom ldan 'das ral pa gcig pa'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD2124E:170b-4: rje btsun ral pa gcig ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2124E:170b-5: shin tu gsang ba'i rtog pa las //
T02TD2124E:170b-6: rnal 'byur ro pa la phan byed pa //
T02TD2124E:170b-7: bla ma'i drin thob dga' ba'i mthus //
T02TD2124E:170b-8: ral pa gcig 'phyang sgrub thabs bri //
T02TD2124E:170b-9: rab tu bsngags pa'i gnas su ni //
T02TD2124E:171a-2: dam tshig tsha dang rab ldan pas //
T02TD2124E:171a-3: dang po stong nyid bsgoms par bya //
T02TD2124E:171a-4: aom sv'a bh'a bshuddha:sarba dharm'a:sva bha ba shuddhonya ham /
T02TD2124E:171a-5: de rjes 'khor lo bcing byas la //
T02TD2124E:171a-6: sna tshogs pad steng nyi zla dang //
T02TD2124E:171a-7: thod pa dang bcas dbugs bral la //
T02TD2124E:171a-8: h'um yig 'bar ba bsam par bya'o //
T02TD2124E:171a-9: h'um bam ma aa ksham don gnyis mdzad de yongs gyur pas //
T02TD2124E:171a-10: rdo rjes mtshan pa'i gri gug can //
T02TD2124E:171a-11: rdo rje'i 'od kyis rnam brgyan pa //
T02TD2124E:171a-12: yi shes sku mchog bsgom pa'o //
T02TD2124E:171a-13: aom a'a:h'um brkyang bskum zhabs gnyis stabs mdzad cing //
T02TD2124E:171a-14: zhal gsum phyag bzhi 'gying bag can //
T02TD2124E:171a-15: rdo rje dang ni thod khrag 'dzin //
T02TD2124E:171a-16: ral gri autpal g-yas dang g-yon //
T02TD2124E:171a-17: nam mkha'i mdog can zhi zhing khro //
T02TD2124E:171a-18: dmar ser ral pa gcig 'phyang ma //
T02TD2124E:171a-19: mi thung gzugs can bzhad mo che //
T02TD2124E:171a-20: rdo rje rin chen rus pas brgyan //
T02TD2124E:171a-21: sangs rgyas lnga yis dbu brgyan cing //
T02TD2124E:171a-22: dus gsum sangs rgyas rtags 'chang ma //
T02TD2124E:171a-23: gar gyi nyams dgus dgyes bzhugs nyid //
T02TD2124E:171a-24: phyag rgya lnga yis rnam brgyan pa'o //
T02TD2124E:171a-25: sku gsung thugs kyi dag pa yis //
T02TD2124E:171a-26: rdo rje'i phyag rgya brtan byas la //
T02TD2124E:171a-27: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dang //
T02TD2124E:171a-28: rdo rje dril bu'i rigs pas sbyang //
T02TD2124E:171a-29: de rjes mchod sogs sngon 'go bas//
T02TD2124E:171a-30: snying rje chen po mdun bzhag ste //
T02TD2124E:171a-31: sa gsum rnam par sbyang pa yi //
T02TD2124E:171a-32: rig sngags rgyal po bzlas par bya //
T02TD2124E:171a-34: ting 'dzin tshogs pa tshang pa yi //
T02TD2124E:171a-35: sgrub pa po ni rab dang ldan //
T02TD2124E:171a-36: bla ma mnyes byed rnal 'byor brtson //
T02TD2124E:171a-37: 'bum phrag bzhi yis dngos grub byed //
T02TD2124E:171a-38: sdig pa thams cad 'jig byed cing //
T02TD2124E:171a-39: don kun sgrub byed gsang sngags 'di //
T02TD2124E:171a-40: de rjes lus can snying brtse bas //
T02TD2124E:171a-41: gtso bo nye bar bya phyir bzlas //
T02TD2124E:171a-42: aom a'a:h'um badzrod bha ba ka ra dzny'a na pra tishtha ta h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD2124E:171a-43: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs rje ba //
T02TD2124E:171a-44: gsang sngags rgyal po rdo rje can //
T02TD2124E:171a-45: ral pa gcig mchog dpal ldan ma //
T02TD2124E:171a-46: de mnyes man ngag 'di yin no //
T02TD2124E:171a-47: dpal bcom ldan 'das ral pa gcig ma'i sgrub thabs slob dpon chen po rol pa'i rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2124E:171a-49: // / rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug ma h'a shr'i dz'a ga ta mi tra a'a na nda r'a dza dang /
T02TD2124E:171b-0: gnubs @171b lo tsa ba mee tri shr'is bsgyur ba'o//
